<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container about-copy">
    <p>Nandrews is a long-established local garage on Shirley Road, serving Southampton drivers with MOT testing, servicing, diagnostics and repairs. The business has been part of the area since 1965, and the focus remains on giving people straightforward help with their vehicles without making the process feel more complicated than it needs to be.</p>
    <p>That matters because many drivers still find garages intimidating. A lot of people are not looking for technical language or pressure. They just want to know what is wrong, what needs doing now, and what the sensible next step is. The aim at Nandrews is to make that feel clear from the first phone call or booking.</p>
    <p>Whether the vehicle needs its yearly MOT, routine servicing, fault finding or repair work, the approach is practical and honest. The garage works with local drivers across Southampton who want reliable workmanship, clear advice and a service they feel comfortable coming back to.</p>
  </div>
</section>
